# Managing Splunk Services

## Using Command Prompt (Administrator)

Navigate to the Splunk binary directory:

```powershell
cd "C:\Program Files\Splunk\bin"
```

### Start Splunk

```powershell
splunk start
```

### Stop Splunk

```powershell
splunk stop
```

### Restart Splunk

```powershell
splunk restart
