# SPL Queries

## Display All Indexed Events

Retrieve all events available across every indexed dataset.

```spl
index=*
```

---

## Count Events by Sourcetype

Display the total number of events grouped by their respective sourcetypes.

```spl
index=* 
| stats count BY sourcetype
```

---

## Analyze Splunk Internal Logs

Retrieve event counts from Splunk's internal logs to monitor platform activity.

```spl
index=_internal
| stats count BY sourcetype
```

